metadata.name: The Giving Cats #1
metadata.description: The Giving Cats are a collection of 5,000 NFT assets living on the Ethereum blockchain. Each of these 5,000 cats is unique in its color, outfit, and appearance, and once minted, it will be 100% owned by you. Our cats cannot be copied, destroyed, or removed. By participating in one of the most meaningful and charitable NFT projects in the world, you'll help build an influential community of cat lovers. Our goal is to expand this community globally.
